{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126634019648180224683417.jpeg/bq7gPhKU8tq8xAOp5IjYWwOrwsizHte0whAciMIQHIg\" alt=\"李蔓瑩Renee隻貓好可愛。（ig@reneebobo）\"><figcaption>李蔓瑩Renee隻貓好可愛。（ig@reneebobo）</figcaption></figure><p>一腳踢做書</p><p>帖文中可見，印刷出的寫真「堆到成山」一樣，相當壯觀！她在帖文中寫道：「這本書終於實體誕生了。回想最初，由文字、約攝、妝、頭、場地、後期、小禮物，自己一個包辦 壓力真的很大(⑉･̆-･̆⑉) 超級感謝各路朋友的協助，感謝當初出版社的邀請，感謝印刷廠的各位才會令這本書真實存在。」專訪丨李蔓瑩欣賞伍允龍坦蕩公開戀情　相差13歲被批唔襯：冇代溝</p><p>李蔓瑩Renee接受《香港01》訪問，她透露今批印刷了近本實體書：「簽咗4個鐘，見到實體書之後，覺得呢幾個月嘅努力同壓力係值得嘅，真係好開心。人最重要嘅三個意義，人生第一本書、同Nigo嘅回憶、自己同買書嘅大家都幫到流浪動物。」</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126635093209780224903741.jpeg/Pk8W-HbenoHDbE0QbYNT4HkXkDaY4bXvc5ZshHOWbIQ\" alt=\"Renee李蔓瑩本寫真集終於推出，啲書堆到成堆山咁！（ig@reneebobo）\"><figcaption>Renee李蔓瑩本寫真集終於推出，啲書堆到成堆山咁！（ig@reneebobo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126635090516905984617053.jpeg/0LgZ8XXgahRbZHMGIN26dP8JZrSLxJ7lbrrqJ2666ic\" alt=\"Renee李蔓瑩推出散文寫真集。（ig@reneebobo）\"><figcaption>Renee李蔓瑩推出散文寫真集。（ig@reneebobo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126635100457930752372168.jpeg/43WkQd4-F_y9mnNj8YM4QUn3T0AewcAFmPQYhpj0GIY\" alt=\"Renee李蔓瑩本寫真集終於推出，啲書堆到成堆山咁！（ig@reneebobo）\"><figcaption>Renee李蔓瑩本寫真集終於推出，啲書堆到成堆山咁！（ig@reneebobo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126635098192875520697843.jpeg/zVVzztzdGzKoBY9V4AMQcSxHbU9pLbe_XVFEDV1RRA0\" alt=\"Renee李蔓瑩推出散文寫真集。（ig@reneebobo）\"><figcaption>Renee李蔓瑩推出散文寫真集。（ig@reneebobo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126635096041066496639480.jpeg/9JJdwJU5JnzCz8JfKVKPqz1Jc8CIpQ7uZ_Krnmfyq54\" alt=\"包裝又幾靚喎。（ig@reneebobo）\"><figcaption>包裝又幾靚喎。（ig@reneebobo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126635093662765056807316.jpeg/souvDofyQE6RIAy7_kPNw8oIxSWnT3vwEZVEyhGVRMo\" alt=\"目測有300本？（ig@reneebobo）\"><figcaption>目測有300本？（ig@reneebobo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126635091292852224964102.jpeg/uf1ur2fvbfdJvWXHiTFzUzja0sdCZQc0ugOwu7oDsLs\" alt=\"包裝又幾靚喎。（ig@reneebobo）\"><figcaption>包裝又幾靚喎。（ig@reneebobo）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260410/1119062658578911232145872.jpeg/JA_aAUu2q3mlwojekj63dV5T4tDigjvxtTxngJA8Z4A\" alt=\"李蔓瑩Renee出散文寫真集！（林迅景 攝）\"><figcaption>李蔓瑩Renee出散文寫真集！（林迅景 攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260410/1119063106648018944743650.jpeg/uBnVhWHofYCIsy5Pj0Oo9inuAhwXVfs8SfqqVkn6qlY\" alt=\"李蔓瑩35歲先出寫真？（ig圖片）\"><figcaption>李蔓瑩35歲先出寫真？（ig圖片）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260410/1119063534748045312586342.jpeg/eyAksznXIHqLl6eYiEqAfgph2KXYbIqASI3gSm2N4Eo\" alt=\"李蔓瑩Renee欣賞男友伍允龍：「好坦蕩，好 Man」。（林迅景 攝）\"><figcaption>李蔓瑩Renee欣賞男友伍允龍：「好坦蕩，好 Man」。（林迅景 攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T15:10:43.685850+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":607,"images":11,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}